title: Senate election to be held on time:Vawda
content:
ISLAMABAD, Dec 29 (APP): Minister for Water Resources Faisal Vawda has said that the government is not going anywhere and Senate election will be held on time.
In his tweet on Tuesday, the minister said, “ Beggars can’t be choosers. Finally Maryam and Molana got a smashing slap on their face from PPP.
What I said a few weeks back came out to be the same that Senate election will be on
time, no resignation. Corrupt Nawaz and Calibri Queen’s dream shattered!”.
